OL,3,CA four-day working week in Wales: The
OL,4,Cpros, cons, and reality
OL,6,FA four-day working week has helped
OL,7,Fimprove productivity and happiness
OL,8,Fwhile prompting a drop in sickness
OL,9,Frates, according to a business owner
OL,10,Fin Cardiff.
OL,12,FIt comes as a working group, set up by
OL,13,Fthe following calls for a pilot in
OL,14,FWales' devolved public services,
OL,15,Freleased their findings on the pros
OL,16,Fand cons of a four-day working week
OL,17,Fafter a year of research.
