OL,3,CA four-day working week in Wales: The
OL,4,Cpros, cons, and reality
OL,6,FThere are two ways to interpret a four-
OL,7,Fday week. It could mean workers who
OL,8,Fusually work five days a week
OL,9,Fcompleting the same number of hours
OL,10,Fover four days, or it could mean a
OL,11,Fshorter working week with the same pay
OL,12,Fas before.
OL,14,FThe working group - established under
OL,15,Fthe Workforce Partnership Council
OL,16,F(WPC) - specifically looked at the
OL,17,Flatter: working a four-day week with
OL,18,Fno loss of pay or benefits.
