OL,3,CA four-day working week in Wales: The
OL,4,Cpros, cons, and reality
OL,6,FBenefits highlights were improved work-
OL,7,Flife balance, reduced risk of burnout,
OL,8,Fbetter physical and mental health,
OL,9,Fimproved recruitment and job
OL,10,Fsatisfaction, greater inclusivity and
OL,11,Fincreased productivity.
OL,13,FHowever, it also identified a number
OL,14,Fof risks associated with the policy,
OL,15,Fincluding the widening of existing
OL,16,Finequalities, financial risks
OL,17,Fassociated with recruiting more
OL,18,Fworkers, undeclared hours of work,
OL,19,Fservice delivery concerns, and team
OL,20,Fmanagement and development risks.
