OL,3,CA four-day working week in Wales: The
OL,4,Cpros, cons, and reality
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government may have said
OL,7,Fthere are "no plans" to introduce a
OL,8,Ffour-day week across the public sector
OL,9,Fin Wales, but that doesn't mean the
OL,10,Fmodel is unworkable for some
OL,11,Findustries.
OL,13,FChelsea Thompson, from Slunks hair
OL,14,Fsalon in Cardiff, introduced a four-
OL,15,Fday working week after lockdown,
OL,16,Fpartly to aid with social distancing.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/17
