OL,3,CA four-day working week in Wales: The
OL,4,Cpros, cons, and reality
OL,6,FChelsea said: "After a few months, we
OL,7,Fnoticed the team seemed much happier,
OL,8,Fproductivity was better, sickness was
OL,9,Fdown, their mental health seemed to be
OL,10,Fbetter and we just thought 'right,
OL,11,Fthis is working, let's see if we can
OL,12,Fdo it long-term'."
OL,14,FThe business made it work by taking on
OL,15,Fmore staff.
