OL,3,CA four-day working week in Wales: The
OL,4,Cpros, cons, and reality
OL,6,FShe continued: "We've opened the salon
OL,7,Fmore days and everyone's kind of on a
OL,8,Fmixed shift. It's always rolling, so
OL,9,Fthey know what they're doing week on
OL,10,Fweek. But, it's just four eight-hour
OL,11,Fdays within a week."
OL,13,FAsked if she would change the model
OL,14,Fnow, she said she wouldn't.J"I think
OL,15,Fthe team all enjoy it far too much,"
OL,16,Fshe said. "I personally enjoy it a lot
OL,17,Fas well. It's just a really nice
OL,18,Fenergy and atmosphere in the salon."
