OL,3,CA four-day working week in Wales: The
OL,4,Cpros, cons, and reality
OL,6,FShe added: "I think each industry are
OL,7,Fgoing to have their own hurdles to get
OL,8,Fover to make this work. It's not going
OL,9,Fto work for everyone unfortunately.
OL,11,F"But, I would really encourage
OL,12,Feveryone to sit down and look if they
OL,13,Fcan possibly make it work - the pros
OL,14,Ffar outweigh the cons, they definitely
OL,15,Fhave for us.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/17
