OL,3,CA four-day working week in Wales: The
OL,4,Cpros, cons, and reality
OL,6,F"The benefits have been that we've got
OL,7,Fnew staff coming in - we've doubled
OL,8,Four numbers in the last four years of
OL,9,Fstaff. Our turnover is a lot less,
OL,10,Fsickness is a lot less and overall
OL,11,Fwellbeing of the team is much better
OL,12,Fas well."
OL,14,FDarren Williams is national officer at
OL,15,FPCS Union, the largest civil service
OL,16,Funion. He was one of those involved in
OL,17,Fthe working group.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/17
