OL,3,CA four-day working week in Wales: The
OL,4,Cpros, cons, and reality
OL,6,FHe said: "Workers in Britain work the
OL,7,Flongest hours anywhere in western
OL,8,FEurope and there are obviously gains
OL,9,Fto be made from things like improved
OL,10,Ftechnology at work, gains in terms of
OL,11,Fa better work-life balance and really
OL,12,Fspreading those gains more widely than
OL,13,Fat present.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/17
