OL,3,CA four-day working week in Wales: The
OL,4,Cpros, cons, and reality
OL,6,F"Unions in the 19th century campaigned
OL,7,Ffor shorter working hours, in the 20th
OL,8,Fcentury for a two-day weekend and in
OL,9,Fmany ways this is the natural
OL,10,Fconclusion to that because it's about
OL,11,Fmaking sure that people's working
OL,12,Flives are more manageable and that
OL,13,Fthey have more time to themselves and
OL,14,Ftheir families."
