OL,3,CA four-day working week in Wales: The
OL,4,Cpros, cons, and reality
OL,6,FAsked how companies can afford to pay
OL,7,Fpeople for working less, Mr Williams
OL,8,Fsaid: "Well, the idea is that
OL,9,Ftechnology meant that there are
OL,10,Fproductivity gains available and it's
OL,11,Fa question of ensuring that those
OL,12,Fgains are spread more evenly among the
OL,13,Fworkforce.
OL,15,F"So what the working group was looking
OL,16,Finto was the possibility of reducing
OL,17,Fworking hours without any reduction in
OL,18,Fpay but on the basis that productivity
OL,19,Fwould be maintained."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/17
