OL,3,CA four-day working week in Wales: The
OL,4,Cpros, cons, and reality
OL,6,FHe added: "There is a risk that the
OL,7,Ffour-day working week or a shorter
OL,8,Fworking week could be introduced in a
OL,9,Fway that's unfair or rather
OL,10,Fexacerbates existing inequalities and
OL,11,Fthat's something that has to be worked
OL,12,Finto any proposal to take it forward.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/17
