OL,3,CA four-day working week in Wales: The
OL,4,Cpros, cons, and reality
OL,6,F"Having said that, nobody has
OL,7,Fsuggested that a four-day working week
OL,8,Fis a panacea for all the problems in
OL,9,Fthe workplace - inequalities, poor pay
OL,10,Fand so on - those are things that
OL,11,Ftrade unions and others are committed
OL,12,Fto addressing. But absolutely there is
OL,13,Fa recognition that there are dangers
OL,14,Fin introducing this in a way that's
OL,15,Fnot properly thought through."
OL,17,FDr Simon Williams, a behavioural
OL,18,Fscientist and public health researcher
OL,19,Fat Swansea University, broadly
OL,20,Fsupports the idea of giving people an
OL,21,Fextra day off per week.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G13/17
