OL,3,CA four-day working week in Wales: The
OL,4,Cpros, cons, and reality
OL,6,FHe said: "There are positive impacts
OL,7,Ffor organisations. People are working
OL,8,Fmore productively because they're
OL,9,Fbeing asked to work lower hours. There
OL,10,Fare also gains from a wellbeing
OL,11,Fperspective, definitely. There's
OL,12,Freduction in sick leave. People are
OL,13,Fworking less hours."
OL,15,FHowever, the psychology lecturer said
OL,16,Fa big issue with a four-day working
OL,17,Fweek would be the "inequality" of some
OL,18,Fworkers reaping the benefits, while it
OL,19,Fwould not be feasible for others to
OL,20,Freduce the number of days they work.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G14/17
