OL,3,CA four-day working week in Wales: The
OL,4,Cpros, cons, and reality
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government said there are
OL,7,F"no plans" to introduce a four-day
OL,8,Fweek across the public sector in Wales.
OL,10,FIt said: "Whilst the working group
OL,11,Fidentified a range of potential
OL,12,Fbenefits, they also highlighted the
OL,13,Fmany complexities involved in adopting
OL,14,Fa four-day week and the impact these
OL,15,Fcould have on a range of groups and
OL,16,Findividuals."
