OL,3,CA four-day working week in Wales: The
OL,4,Cpros, cons, and reality
OL,6,FJoel James MS, Welsh Conservatives'
OL,7,Fshadow minister for social
OL,8,Fpartnership, said: "The major problem
OL,9,Fof the four-day working week is that
OL,10,Fit cannot be rolled out across every
OL,11,Fsector, meaning that it will create a
OL,12,Ftwo-tier working environment.
OL,14,F"The Welsh Conservatives propose that
OL,15,Fthe same benefits of a four-day
OL,16,Fworking week can be obtained by
OL,17,Fimproving the flexibility workers to
OL,18,Ftake time off to balance family life
OL,19,Fand other commitments."
